				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Im wondering what happens if you fail on making the pike itself, do you lose the forging hammer?  They are very expensive, and if theres a chance it could be lost, I might save the money and get a different weapon.<BR>
<BR>
Also, to those of you having trouble finding Froglok Bounders, heres a spot where I had a lot of luck with them.  Saw 2 in a few hours, both had froglok bounder javelins.  Swamp of no hope, loc: <BR>
<BR>
1434.09, 1487.07, 37.96  (All posotive)<BR>
<BR>
Its a small hill.  If you point away from cabilis, sometimes blues/whites to a lvl 10 will wander past to your left.  Thats the path the bounders were on.  I just killed anything that wandered past I could take, and eventually got the bounders.  You can also go out farther somone told me and find them, some outpost camp.  The swamp gets dangerous very quickly however, I died looking for the camp.  There are also the occasional nasty thing that wanders by the spot I mentioned, so keep an eye out.  Remember if you dont see any for a while, your going to have to kill something to get them to spawn, probly.
